<p>Friday 8 June</p>
<p>Fine.<br/>Trip down to Albert today on the bike<br/>Since the 2nd inst. nothing of any note has been occurring, other the daily cricket matches.<br/>We are now a reserve division in the 3rd Army.  All units have orders to make use of afternoons by playing cricket.<br/>Despatch Riding duties continue</p>
